---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout title="Work | Henry Percy">
	<main>
		<section class="prose prose-stone dark:prose-invert">
			<h1 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold leading-none tracking-tight md:text-4xl">Work</h1>
			<p>I'm a Junior Software Developer currently turning complex ideas into smooth digital experiences on the web.</p>
			<hr>
			<article>
				<h2 class="!mb-1 flex items-baseline gap-2"><span>Rework Digital</span> <a href="https://rework.digital" target="_blank"><svg class="shrink-0 fill-stone-700 dark:fill-stone-300 hover:fill-black hover:dark:fill-white transition-all" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="m16 8.4l-8.9 8.9q-.275.275-.7.275t-.7-.275q-.275-.275-.275-.7t.275-.7L14.6 7H7q-.425 0-.713-.288T6 6q0-.425.288-.713T7 5h10q.425 0 .713.288T18 6v10q0 .425-.288.713T17 17q-.425 0-.713-.288T16 16V8.4Z"/></svg></a></h2>
				<p class="font-light text-stone-400 dark:text-stone-500">Junior Software Developer, 2023 - 24</p>
				<p>I currently specialise in developing bespoke digital experiences for e-commerce, primarily using JavaScript, <a href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank">Astro</a>, <a href="https://vuejs.org/" target="_blank">Vue</a>, and <a href="https://tailwindcss.com/" target="_blank">Tailwind</a>. This role has given me my first experience in a production environment, utilising TDD to create reliable and efficient web applications. Beyond front-end development, my work also encompasses back-end projects, particularly in building REST APIs with PHP, <a href="https://laravel.com/" target="_blank">Laravel</a>, and MySQL.</p>
			</article>
			<hr>
			<article>
				<h2 class="!mb-1 flex items-baseline gap-2"><span>Tria Recruitment</span> <a href="https://www.triarecruitment.com" target="_blank"><svg class="shrink-0 fill-stone-700 dark:fill-stone-300 hover:fill-black hover:dark:fill-white transition-all" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="m16 8.4l-8.9 8.9q-.275.275-.7.275t-.7-.275q-.275-.275-.275-.7t.275-.7L14.6 7H7q-.425 0-.713-.288T6 6q0-.425.288-.713T7 5h10q.425 0 .713.288T18 6v10q0 .425-.288.713T17 17q-.425 0-.713-.288T16 16V8.4Z"/></svg></a></h2>
				<p class="font-light text-stone-400 dark:text-stone-500">Delivery Consultant, 2021 - 22</p>
				<p>Working as a Delivery Consultant I focused on hiring professionals such as Software Engineers, Product Managers, and Technical Leaders. This role deepened my understanding of how software teams organise themselves and honed my stakeholder management skills. Crucially, it was through this role that I realised my potential for a career in Software Development, guiding my professional transition.</p>
			</article>
			<hr>
			<article>
				<h2 class="!mb-1 flex items-baseline gap-2"><span>Faculty of Environment & Technology (UWE)</span> <a href="https://www.uwe.ac.uk" target="_blank"><svg class="shrink-0 fill-stone-700 dark:fill-stone-300 hover:fill-black hover:dark:fill-white transition-all" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="m16 8.4l-8.9 8.9q-.275.275-.7.275t-.7-.275q-.275-.275-.275-.7t.275-.7L14.6 7H7q-.425 0-.713-.288T6 6q0-.425.288-.713T7 5h10q.425 0 .713.288T18 6v10q0 .425-.288.713T17 17q-.425 0-.713-.288T16 16V8.4Z"/></svg></a></h2>
				<p class="font-light text-stone-400 dark:text-stone-500">Software Developer, 2021</p>
				<p>During a six-month contract, I focused on constructing environmental sensors using <a href="https://www.arduino.cc/" target="_blank">Arduino</a> and C++ libraries. This project aimed to develop cost-effective and expendable alternatives to high-priced volatile compound and decibel sensors.</p>
			</article>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
